<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset your Password</title>

    <style>
        .username {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .message-heading {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .info {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .info-span {
            font-weight: normal;
        }
        .from-reg {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }
        .from {
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>    
    <div class="username">Dear {{ fullName }},</div>
    <div class="message">We received a request to reset the password associated with your account on Wallet watcher. If you did not request this change, please disregard this email.</div>
    
    <div class="info">To reset your password, please click on the following link: <a href="{{ verificationCode }}">Password Reset Link</a></div>
    <div class="message">Please note that this link will be valid for 30 minutes from the time this email was sent. If you do not reset your password within this timeframe, you will need to submit another password reset request.</div>
    
    <div class="info">If the link doesn't work, copy and paste the following URL into your browser's address bar: <a href="{{ verificationCode }}">Password Reset Link</a></div>
    
    <div class="message">Once you have accessed the link, you will be prompted to create a new password for your account. Please ensure that your new password is unique and not easily guessable.</div>
    
    <div class="message">If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at {{ custContactEmailId }}.</div>
    <div class="message">Thank you for using Wallet watcher.</div>
    
    <div class="from-reg">Best regards,</div>
    <div class="from">Team Wallet watcher</div>
</body>
</html>